@startuml C4_Ops_Deployment
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

title YAWL Operations - Deployment Pipeline

Boundary(ci, "CI/CD Pipeline") {
    Component(git_push, "Git Push", "Source", "Code commit")
    Component(build_job, "Build Job", "Maven", "Compile & test")
    Component(test_job, "Test Job", "JUnit", "Run all tests")
    Component(guard_gate, "Guard Gate (H)", "Validation", "h-guards check")
    Component(invariant_gate, "Invariant Gate (Q)", "Validation", "q-invariants check")
}

Boundary(staging, "Staging Deployment") {
    Component(stage_build, "Staging Build", "Container", "Docker image")
    Component(stage_deploy, "Staging Deploy", "Kubernetes", "Deploy to staging")
    Component(stage_test, "Staging Tests", "E2E", "Full integration test")
    Component(stage_approval, "Approval", "Manual", "Human approval")
}

Boundary(production, "Production Deployment") {
    Component(prod_build, "Prod Build", "Container", "Official release")
    Component(prod_canary, "Canary Deploy", "Traffic", "10% traffic")
    Component(prod_monitor, "Monitoring", "Health", "SLA tracking")
    Component(prod_full, "Full Deploy", "Traffic", "100% traffic")
    Component(prod_rollback, "Rollback Ready", "Safety", "Quick rollback")
}

git_push --> build_job: Triggers
build_job --> test_job: On success
test_job --> guard_gate: On success
guard_gate --> invariant_gate: On success
invariant_gate --> stage_build: On success

stage_build --> stage_deploy: Builds image
stage_deploy --> stage_test: Deploys to
stage_test --> stage_approval: If tests pass
stage_approval --> prod_build: Approves

prod_build --> prod_canary: Canary release
prod_canary --> prod_monitor: 10% traffic
prod_monitor --> prod_full: If healthy
prod_full --> prod_rollback: Always ready

Note as N1
Deployment Pipeline:
1. Git push → builds code
2. Run tests → must pass
3. Run guards → no TODO/mock
4. Run invariants → real code only
5. Deploy to staging → full E2E
6. Manual approval
7. Canary deploy to prod (10%)
8. Monitor SLAs
9. Full production rollout
10. Rollback always ready

Approval Gates: 2 (after invariants, after E2E)
End note

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
